name: Commander Brandei
Lore: 'Technical Services Officer of the Fleet Support Branch. Responsible for keeping Executor''s 12 TIE squadrons serviced and combat ready. Just received transfer to Judicator.',
Text: 'Adds 2 to power of anything he pilots. Once during each of your control phases, when aboard a Star Destroyer or at any docking bay, may use 1 Force to take one TIE into hand from Reserve Deck; reshuffle.',
